dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Alan Jones. May I please have your name?
Hi, my name is Marie Kelly.
Nice to meet you, Marie. Could you kindly provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's two zero three eight one.
Thank you, Marie. Can you also confirm your date of birth for verification purposes, please?
Yes, it's the twentieth of March, nineteen eighty-five.
Great, thank you for the information. Is there anything specific you would like assistance with today, Marie?
I wanted to add a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, we can help with that. Thank you for sharing, Marie. Let's get started on updating your policy. We appreciate your time.
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a wonderful day!
